description: Love to bake! Cakes, Cookies, Gobs, Cupcakes, Pumpkin Rolls, and more!We start from scratch using only the finest quality ingredients such as Madagascar bourbon vanilla, real sweet cream butter, fresh fruit, and our freshly made caramel.Visit us and try our delicious cupcakes, cookies, cake push pops, or our famous pumpkin rolls.We make cakes and take special orders, too!So come see us and Let us Bake You Happy!
name: Hummingbird Sweet Shop
